'''Atom''' is an open-source, graphical text editor developed by GitHub. It is called the, "Hackable text editor for the 21st Century" by its developers. It is built on the Electron framework, written in CSS, CoffeeScript, JavaScript and Less and is packaged by GitHub for 64-bit Debian and Red Hat Linux, macOS and Windows.

